TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {20214=A second man has died following a crash on Highway 35 last week. Drew Mason, 26, of Sparta, was flown to the University of Cincinnati Hospital following the crash. Mason was pronounced dead by the Hamilton County Coroner Oct. 9 at the University of Cincinnati Hospital. Alcohol is suspected to be a factor in the crash that also killed Justin Renfro, 24, of Owenton.
